-- Toyota sales off 41.9 percent in April
-- 
-- Fri May 1, 2009 2:30pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/05/01/us-toyota-sb-idUSTRE5405AS20090501

 

 (Reuters) - TOYOTA MOTOR CORP reported April sales on Friday. 

 Highlights: * says US April sales decreased 41.9 percent on an adjusted basis * says April month-end sales of 126,540 vehicles